They all end up in the same place.

519
01:02:25.395 --> 01:02:27.271
The same shallow ditch.

520
01:02:28.106 --> 01:02:29.273
Under the same river.

521
01:02:30.733 --> 01:02:32.235
Fill it With rocks.

522
01:02:39.492 --> 01:02:41.369
That's the proof.

523
01:02:41.536 --> 01:02:43.955
If you choose to follow us.
you follow us.

524
01:02:44.122 --> 01:02:45.623
Simple as that.

525
01:02:47.792 --> 01:02:49.794
They burn out real fast.

526
01:02:51.337 --> 01:02:53.548
I see it in Uco.

527
01:02:55.258 --> 01:02:57.927
I've tried to ignore it.
but it didn't work.

528
01:02:58.094 --> 01:03:00.221
I know Uco has that fire.

529
01:03:01.514 --> 01:03:07.478
I had to lose a lot in my life before I
could truly see that that was important.

530
01:03:08.146 --> 01:03:10.773
I don't want the same
to happen to my boy.

531
01:03:12.191 --> 01:03:14.068
He won't. sir.

532
01:03:14.235 --> 01:03:17.155
The time I've known him.
he speaks nothing but highly of you.

533
01:03:18.823 --> 01:03:20.950
I hope you're right.

534
01:03:21.117 --> 01:03:23.494
But I know what my gut tells me.

535
01:03:25.037 --> 01:03:28.749
Lately you're his shadow.

536
01:03:28.916 --> 01:03:31.085
So take care of him.

537
01:03:31.252 --> 01:03:35.256
If you see anything weird. you tell me.

538
01:03:36.466 --> 01:03:39.302
Otherwise. it's like I said...

539
01:03:39.469 --> 01:03:43.222
falling in the same ditch
under the same river.

540
01:03:46.184 --> 01:03:48.895
I hope for your sake you can swim.

541
01:03:53.566 --> 01:03:57.737
Toss them back in.
Nothing tastes good here.

542
01:04:24.138 --> 01:04:27.391
The main difference between you and I
can be defined by one word.

543
01:04:28.059 --> 01:04:29.769
Legacy-

544
01:04:31.145 --> 01:04:36.275
Every step I take is a step forward
for my group and family.

545
01:04:36.442 --> 01:04:40.363
Every step that you take...

546
01:04:40.530 --> 01:04:44.325
is cloaked
in the shadow of your father.

547
01:04:46.118 --> 01:04:48.120
In my life...

548
01:04:49.163 --> 01:04:52.708
I never have to
follow anyone's rules.

549
01:04:54.001 --> 01:04:57.213
No expectations of who I should become.

550
01:04:59.131 --> 01:05:01.217
No rules to abide by.

551
01:05:03.970 --> 01:05:05.596
My father...

552
01:05:06.889 --> 01:05:10.518
he was a fucking road sweeper.

553
01:05:10.685 --> 01:05:15.147
Shining shoes would have made me
a success story compared to him.

554
01:05:15.940 --> 01:05:17.858
So. yes...

555
01:05:18.025 --> 01:05:20.444
you and I.
we couldn't be more different.

556
01:05:21.404 --> 01:05:24.782
But deep inside.
our ambitions are the same.

557
01:05:25.074 --> 01:05:28.619
After all. you came here
of your own accord.

558
01:05:40.673 --> 01:05:43.718
Now we've eaten well.
drank good wine...

559
01:05:43.884 --> 01:05:47.013
there's one thing
that you should know about me.

560
01:05:47.888 --> 01:05:50.808
If I'm the type of person
who likes to impose my will...

561
01:05:50.975 --> 01:05:53.894
I would've already
pointed a gun at your head.

562
01:05:57.648 --> 01:06:00.401
But no. that's not me.

563
01:06:00.943 --> 01:06:02.820
Not today at least.

564
01:06:06.907 --> 01:06:09.285
Today I'm offering you a gift.

565
01:06:11.704 --> 01:06:13.247
An opportunity.

566
01:06:15.916 --> 01:06:19.754
Something that has never been
given to you by your father.

567
01:06:21.380 --> 01:06:22.423
Please.

568
01:06:59.710 --> 01:07:02.338
Those prison gates opened
and not one person...

569
01:07:02.505 --> 01:07:05.174
from your group was there
to pick them up.

570
01:07:06.425 --> 01:07:08.094
I was surprised.

571
01:07:10.179 --> 01:07:12.223
Imagine...

572
01:07:12.390 --> 01:07:16.519
how surprised they were when
they found out I picked them up...

573
01:07:16.686 --> 01:07:18.646
and brought them here...

574
01:07:18.813 --> 01:07:21.357
for you.

575
01:07:27.238 --> 01:07:29.198
That's my gift.

576
01:07:30.741 --> 01:07:32.993
I give you the opportunity...

577
01:07:34.745 --> 01:07:36.956
to claim revenge.

578
01:07:51.554 --> 01:07:52.555
And after that?

579
01:07:55.933 --> 01:07:57.935
We talk business.

580
01:08:07.611 --> 01:08:08.946
Just so you know.

581
01:08:09.113 --> 01:08:12.658
- If you need financial help...
- I need labor.

582
01:08:12.825 --> 01:08:15.411
Oh. that I can do.

583
01:08:15.578 --> 01:08:17.496
So. what do you want exactly?

584
01:08:17.663 --> 01:08:20.124
I've got my eye on this patch of land.

585
01:08:20.791 --> 01:08:22.877
Whose land?

586
01:08:23.502 --> 01:08:26.213
That's why I need your help.

587
01:08:28.883 --> 01:08:31.135
There are only two possibilities.

588
01:08:31.969 --> 01:08:33.220
I'm sorry.

589
01:08:33.387 --> 01:08:35.347
But with all due respect.

590
01:08:35.514 --> 01:08:37.466
If I wanted to rent a patch of land...

591
01:08:37.533 --> 01:08:40.786
fair and square.
I'd be meeting your father.

592
01:08:41.645 --> 01:08:43.272
Not you.

593
01:08:46.275 --> 01:08:47.943
It belongs to the Japanese.

594
01:09:00.539 --> 01:09:03.626
The spot is perfect
for me to start my business.

595
01:09:04.835 --> 01:09:06.555
Then why are you meeting with me?

596
01:09:08.214 --> 01:09:10.508
It's their land.

597
01:09:17.598 --> 01:09:19.767
My father would never allow it.

598
01:09:19.934 --> 01:09:22.478
He would never do anything
to disrupt the truce.

599
01:09:22.645 --> 01:09:24.647
I'm not interested
in what your father thinks.

600
01:09:24.814 --> 01:09:27.650
I need your support.
and if I can be frank...

601
01:09:27.817 --> 01:09:30.194
it seems you need my support also.

602
01:09:30.778 --> 01:09:32.154
What do you mean?

603
01:09:33.239 --> 01:09:36.408
I heard the top brass aren't happy
with your father anymore.

604
01:09:37.451 --> 01:09:40.996
Times are changing. The Goto family
is starting to make connections.

605
01:09:41.163 --> 01:09:43.415
Top connections.

606
01:09:43.582 --> 01:09:46.669
When your father leaves the office.
he goes home. he sleeps.

607
01:09:46.836 --> 01:09:50.881
Meanwhile. Goto's boy is taking Reza
to a club and partying.

608
01:09:51.048 --> 01:09:52.216
Just so you know.

609
01:09:52.383 --> 01:09:57.429
It's easy to sway a cop or a politician
with a little cash and a lot of pussy.

610
01:10:01.809 --> 01:10:03.769
What do you want'?

611
01:10:04.186 --> 01:10:07.398
Give me your word.
and I'll put an end to the truce.

612
01:10:07.565 --> 01:10:12.695
Put your faith in me and I'll tip the
odds in your favor when the war begins.

613
01:10:12.862 --> 01:10:14.071
Let them all see...

614
01:10:14.238 --> 01:10:19.159
how you took charge and made your
family bigger than it's ever been.

615
01:10:19.326 --> 01:10:22.538
And you? What's in it for you?

616
01:10:24.164 --> 01:10:26.709
Everyone has their limit.

617
01:10:26.876 --> 01:10:29.565
After we take over
Goto's territory. I just

618
01:10:29.607 --> 01:10:32.214
want a small patch
that I can use freely.

619
01:10:32.923 --> 01:10:35.175
Without having to pay anyone.

620
01:10:35.342 --> 01:10:36.552
No questions asked.

621
01:10:38.971 --> 01:10:42.391
And how do you propose
to start a war between us?

622
01:10:42.558 --> 01:10:45.085
Not a drop of blood has been spilled
in over 10 years.

623
01:10:45.152 --> 01:10:46.904
Well. that would have to change.

624
01:10:56.488 --> 01:10:58.282
Good boy.

625
01:11:37.863 --> 01:11:41.367
If you expect my father to put
his men to war with the Gotos...

626
01:11:41.533 --> 01:11:44.536
it'll take a lot more
than just the death of foot soldiers.

627
01:11:44.703 --> 01:11:48.374
I already have someone in mind.

628
01:13:55.334 --> 01:13:57.169
Okay. so same time next month.

629
01:13:57.711 --> 01:13:59.963
Dwi. wait.

630
01:14:01.298 --> 01:14:02.298
What is it?

631
01:14:03.049 --> 01:14:06.094
- What about Karim?
- What about him?

632
01:14:06.260 --> 01:14:07.386
Dwi...

633
01:14:07.553 --> 01:14:08.888
you promised.

634
01:14:09.055 --> 01:14:11.599
I said when the time is right.

635
01:14:11.766 --> 01:14:12.809
Not yet.

636
01:14:17.563 --> 01:14:19.899
His friends come here often. 'Koso.

637
01:14:21.442 --> 01:14:24.779
Do you think he wants to explain to them
that this is his father?

638
01:14:25.279 --> 01:14:28.991
You don't have to do that. I get it.

639
01:14:29.158 --> 01:14:33.454
- But I haven't seen him since he was...
- Yeah. and whose choice was that?

640
01:14:33.621 --> 01:14:36.791
Yours. right? You're the one
who chose to do what you do.

641
01:14:37.959 --> 01:14:40.002
To support you.

642
01:14:40.169 --> 01:14:43.506
There are millions of fathers in the
world supporting their families.

643
01:14:43.673 --> 01:14:46.175
Only they don't come home
with blood on their hands.

644
01:14:46.342 --> 01:14:49.345
Do you even realize that what you do
is so fucking disgusting?

645
01:14:50.972 --> 01:14:53.933
- I'm not a smart man.
- No. you're not!

646
01:14:57.687 --> 01:14:59.438
But you used to be a good person.

647
01:15:00.815 --> 01:15:03.943
That means that I still have the right
to see my son. right?

648
01:15:05.194 --> 01:15:08.030
That's the thing. you don't.

649
01:15:08.197 --> 01:15:09.240
Not like this.

650
01:15:10.533 --> 01:15:13.369
And I don't want to hear anymore
about you wanting to change.

651
01:15:13.536 --> 01:15:17.123
Because it's been 15 years already.
and I barely recognize you anymore.

652
01:15:37.310 --> 01:15:40.563
I'm sorry. I have to go.

653
01:15:41.939 --> 01:15:44.066
As always.

654
01:16:46.045 --> 01:16:47.380
Crazy.

655
01:16:47.546 --> 01:16:50.383
Seems anyone can get in here
these days.

656
01:16:50.549 --> 01:16:52.051
Way back this place had class.

657
01:16:52.218 --> 01:16:54.637
But now you see
white guys walking around in sandals...

658
01:16:54.804 --> 01:16:58.224
drinking beer and fucking cheap skanks
in the toilets. like fucking animals.

659
01:16:58.391 --> 01:17:00.768
It's a fucking disgrace.

660
01:17:00.935 --> 01:17:04.230
Everything has to be restarted from
the beginning. Starting from us.

661
01:17:04.397 --> 01:17:05.856
Like it was before.

662
01:17:06.691 --> 01:17:09.902
Back then. if my father turned up.
the room would freeze.

663
01:17:10.069 --> 01:17:11.821
They'd fear him.

664
01:17:11.988 --> 01:17:13.948
Because they knew.
he could do anything.

665
01:17:14.407 --> 01:17:16.450
Times change.

666
01:17:16.617 --> 01:17:20.454
They may not fear him like they used to.

667
01:17:20.621 --> 01:17:23.040
But your father
hasn't lost that fire in his stomach.

668
01:17:23.207 --> 01:17:27.295
He just learned how to control it.
They respect him now.

669
01:17:27.461 --> 01:17:29.297
He doesn't need fear anymore.

670
01:17:29.463 --> 01:17:32.550
He has their respect
and that's what counts the most.

671
01:17:32.717 --> 01:17:33.926
It used to count.

672
01:17:34.093 --> 01:17:36.846
Used to. Not anymore.

673
01:17:37.013 --> 01:17:39.390
Times change faster than you think.

674
01:17:39.557 --> 01:17:42.435
We got people now who don't give a shit
about back then.

675
01:17:42.601 --> 01:17:44.061
They only care about now.

676
01:17:44.228 --> 01:17:47.064
Respect?
That doesn't mean shit to them.

677
01:17:47.231 --> 01:17:51.068
That ain't new. We faced punks like that
more times than I care to remember.

678
01:17:51.485 --> 01:17:53.195
Trust me...

679
01:17:53.362 --> 01:17:55.406
they don't last.

680
01:17:56.365 --> 01:17:59.869
And when it's your turn to take the
reins you'll see for yourself.

681
01:18:00.036 --> 01:18:03.497
They'll burn and fall in front of you
just like they did for your father.

682
01:18:05.166 --> 01:18:06.876
That same fire is in you.

683
01:18:07.043 --> 01:18:09.253
I've seen it ever since
you were a child.

684
01:18:10.463 --> 01:18:11.964
Don't ever lose it.

685
01:18:12.131 --> 01:18:14.008
Learn to control it.

686
01:18:14.175 --> 01:18:17.678
If you do. one day you'll become
as great as your father.

687
01:18:22.141 --> 01:18:23.893
'Koso...

688
01:18:24.060 --> 01:18:26.645
you've always been
a good friend to us.

689
01:18:26.812 --> 01:18:28.939
Your father
has always taken good care of me.

690
01:18:30.524 --> 01:18:32.526
To family.

691
01:18:40.117 --> 01:18:41.952
I'll be right back. gotta piss.

692
01:24:51.780 --> 01:24:55.242
The Chinks say they saw the Japs
attacking 'Koso in that alleyway.

693
01:24:55.409 --> 01:24:57.077
Can you believe that shit?

694
01:24:57.619 --> 01:25:01.081
After all this time. they fuck us
like this? We have to respond!

695
01:25:01.248 --> 01:25:04.293
Busting some heads and going to war
are two very different things.

696
01:25:06.754 --> 01:25:08.630
Prakoso's line of work
made him enemies.

697
01:25:08.797 --> 01:25:11.759
Not just the Gotos.
Hell. even the Chinese wanted his head.

698
01:25:12.259 --> 01:25:14.678
This wasn't the first time
he'd been under attack.

699
01:25:15.554 --> 01:25:17.055
Sadly it was the last.

700
01:25:19.641 --> 01:25:22.060
- Where the fuck have you been?
- What happened?

701
01:25:23.854 --> 01:25:25.564
After everything he did for us...

702
01:25:25.731 --> 01:25:27.733
this is how we repay him?

703
01:25:27.900 --> 01:25:31.570
All 'Koso ever cared for in the world
was his wife...

704
01:25:31.737 --> 01:25:33.363
and kid.

705
01:25:34.740 --> 01:25:39.536
He had no time
for making things personal.

706
01:25:39.703 --> 01:25:42.414
So. from now. our duty
is to take care of his family.

707
01:25:42.581 --> 01:25:44.875
But we will not retaliate.

708
01:25:50.422 --> 01:25:51.673
Are you kidding me?

709
01:25:52.049 --> 01:25:54.676
Eka. talk some sense into him.

710
01:25:54.843 --> 01:25:56.804
We're losing our hold here.

711
01:25:57.888 --> 01:25:59.014
Sir...

712
01:25:59.181 --> 01:26:01.642
we have ruled this territory
for over 30 years!

713
01:26:01.809 --> 01:26:05.395
And my decision on this
will see us through 30 more!

714
01:26:05.562 --> 01:26:07.022
Stand down.

715
01:26:07.189 --> 01:26:09.525
Cool off! Relax.

716
01:26:13.028 --> 01:26:14.613
You should remember...

717
01:26:14.780 --> 01:26:17.282
your place.

718
01:26:21.078 --> 01:26:22.412
<i>Um.!</i>

719
01:26:27.042 --> 01:26:28.335
Yuda...

720
01:26:31.296 --> 01:26:33.841
watch over him. take him out...

721
01:26:34.007 --> 01:26:36.593
make him forget about this.
find him a girl.

722
01:26:36.760 --> 01:26:38.637
So he'll get his mind off this.

723
01:26:40.430 --> 01:26:41.974
Yes. boss.

724
01:26:52.860 --> 01:26:55.195
Unbelievable.

725
01:26:58.073 --> 01:26:59.324
Eka...

726
01:27:02.536 --> 01:27:04.329
this is no good.

727
01:27:05.163 --> 01:27:07.249
No good at all.

728
01:27:12.588 --> 01:27:13.839
<i>Um.!</i>

729
01:27:14.923 --> 01:27:16.466
<i>Um.!</i>

730
01:27:18.474 --> 01:27:21.074
- What's wrong?
- Who the fuck do you think you are?

731
01:27:21.138 --> 01:27:22.222
Your father's right.

732
01:27:22.389 --> 01:27:25.434
If you rush into this it won't help.
it will make things worse.

733
01:27:25.601 --> 01:27:27.603
Well. you've grown all of a sudden.

734
01:27:27.769 --> 01:27:29.396
This is a shitty situation...

735
01:27:29.563 --> 01:27:32.003
but you have to refrain yourself.
I've lost control before.

736
01:27:32.107 --> 01:27:34.368
And look where it got me.

737
01:27:34.435 --> 01:27:37.695
Look where it got you? It got you a
fucking penthouse suite that I pay for.

738
01:27:37.781 --> 01:27:40.041
I'm just trying to help.
I know how much your father...

739
01:27:40.083 --> 01:27:41.591
Shut the fuck up!

740
01:27:41.658 --> 01:27:43.702
Who the fuck do you think you are?

741
01:27:43.869 --> 01:27:46.038
You think you know my father?

742
01:27:46.204 --> 01:27:47.998
You mean nothing to him.

743
01:27:48.165 --> 01:27:50.792
We only owed you and we paid it back.

744
01:27:50.959 --> 01:27:54.296
After that.
we're just going to cut you free.

745
01:27:54.463 --> 01:27:57.466
What? Did you expect more?

746
01:27:58.300 --> 01:27:59.843
Go fuck yourself.

747
01:28:15.776 --> 01:28:18.487
<i>- Did we get the</i> okay?
<i>- Fuck the okay.</i>

748
01:28:18.654 --> 01:28:20.572
<i>Just do it.</i>

749
01:29:00.779 --> 01:29:02.197
Do it.

750
01:29:07.995 --> 01:29:10.622
<i>Time for work.</i>

751
01:29:10.914 --> 01:29:12.249
<i>How many?</i>

752
01:29:13.166 --> 01:29:14.251
<i>A few.</i>

753
01:34:12.590 --> 01:34:14.718
Please. have mercy.

754
01:36:04.869 --> 01:36:06.079
Give me the ball.

755
01:36:18.591 --> 01:36:19.759
That was a mistake.

756
01:36:21.219 --> 01:36:23.471
No. wait. don't!

757
01:36:25.807 --> 01:36:27.142
No!

758
01:36:54.836 --> 01:36:57.297
- Where to?
- Tanah Abang.

759
01:39:06.884 --> 01:39:08.386
Enough.

760
01:39:09.637 --> 01:39:10.972
Now...

761
01:39:11.139 --> 01:39:13.391
everything has to stop.

762
01:39:15.018 --> 01:39:17.103
Mr. Goto.

763
01:39:17.520 --> 01:39:19.397
Mr. Bangun.

764
01:39:19.564 --> 01:39:21.274
We acknowledge...

765
01:39:22.942 --> 01:39:24.611
this conflict...

766
01:39:24.777 --> 01:39:27.989
between your groups...

767
01:39:28.156 --> 01:39:31.034
is the first one in 10 years.

768
01:39:32.535 --> 01:39:35.705
There are many casualties.

769
01:39:37.457 --> 01:39:40.627
If this continues...

770
01:39:41.669 --> 01:39:44.255
we will disband both of your groups.

771
01:40:19.832 --> 01:40:21.167
Enough!

772
01:40:21.334 --> 01:40:23.127
Only a fool...

773
01:40:23.294 --> 01:40:26.547
argues for the pride of a dead man.

774
01:40:28.424 --> 01:40:29.801
Mr. Goto...

775
01:40:29.967 --> 01:40:30.968
(mm)' apologies.

776
01:40:32.387 --> 01:40:33.680
It's fine.

777
01:40:35.765 --> 01:40:38.267
I accept full responsibility
for all that has happened.

778
01:40:38.434 --> 01:40:39.769
What?

779
01:40:40.728 --> 01:40:44.482
It seems decisions have been made
by members of my organization...

780
01:40:44.649 --> 01:40:46.192
who are less intelligent...

781
01:40:46.359 --> 01:40:47.985
and less experienced.

782
01:40:48.152 --> 01:40:49.779
For that I can only apologize.

783
01:40:49.946 --> 01:40:51.989
And for all that has happened
this past week.

784
01:40:52.156 --> 01:40:53.700
I will pay all the damages.

785
01:40:53.866 --> 01:40:56.786
To prevent bloodshed
between our families.

786
01:40:58.996 --> 01:41:02.917
Thank you for your swift resolution.

787
01:41:03.084 --> 01:41:06.504
Yeah. Now. gentlemen.
if you'll excuse me.

788
01:41:06.671 --> 01:41:08.715
I have to go back to my organization.

789
01:41:08.881 --> 01:41:10.425
Of course.

790
01:41:10.591 --> 01:41:12.260
Excuse me.

791
01:42:32.632 --> 01:42:35.343
<i>I heard what happened. are you okay?</i>

792
01:42:35.510 --> 01:42:37.762
What the fuck is going on?

793
01:42:37.929 --> 01:42:40.807
Why are the cops attacking me?
Who the fuck made that call?

794
01:42:40.973 --> 01:42:42.683
<i>Calm down.</i>

795
01:42:42.850 --> 01:42:46.562
<i>So far everything seems to suggest
this was purely territorial.</i>

796
01:42:46.729 --> 01:42:49.023
<i>Seems Reza has his men
supporting the Goto family.</i>

797
01:42:49.190 --> 01:42:51.943
<i>- Pull me out now!
- I'm afraid I can't do that.</i>

798
01:42:52.819 --> 01:42:55.321
What do you mean you can't?
What have I not witnessed?

799
01:42:55.488 --> 01:42:57.281
Murder. extortion. bribery?

800
01:42:57.448 --> 01:42:58.616
<i>Corruption.</i>

801
01:42:58.783 --> 01:43:02.495
<i>You were never investigating Bangun.
you knew that.</i>

802
01:43:02.662 --> 01:43:05.248
<i>We want the cops they pay.</i>

803
01:43:05.414 --> 01:43:08.459
<i>You think you're alone in this?
This isn't your show.</i>

804
01:43:08.626 --> 01:43:10.628
<i>None of us are heroes.</i>

805
01:43:10.795 --> 01:43:14.757
<i>We're all caught in a big fucking web.</i>

806
01:43:14.924 --> 01:43:16.300
<i>Listen.</i>

807
01:43:16.467 --> 01:43:19.095
<i>Your identity is safe.</i>

808
01:43:49.967 --> 01:43:52.767
<i>Yuda. where the fuck have you been?
I've been trying to reach you.</i>

809
01:43:52.820 --> 01:43:55.598
<i>Get your ass to the office now
and get Uco the fuck out.</i>

810
01:43:55.664 --> 01:43:56.984
<i>I can't hold back Bangun anymore.</i>

811
01:44:22.909 --> 01:44:27.496
Do you realize how many men
we lost just to play your fucking game?

812
01:44:29.999 --> 01:44:31.959
Everything I've built was for you.

813
01:44:32.126 --> 01:44:35.463
Everything was for you!
And you brought it to the ground.

814
01:44:35.630 --> 01:44:38.299
You destroyed it completely.

815
01:44:38.507 --> 01:44:40.801
And for what?

816
01:44:42.511 --> 01:44:44.555
For what?

817
01:44:47.308 --> 01:44:49.018
Tell me why.

818
01:44:49.852 --> 01:44:52.021
Come on. tell me.

819
01:44:52.188 --> 01:44:53.189
For what?

820
01:44:53.356 --> 01:44:56.067
Please. Dad. please...
Listen to me... Dad. please...

821
01:44:56.233 --> 01:44:58.152
Dad. listen.

822
01:44:58.319 --> 01:45:01.030
- For what?
- Fuck!

823
01:45:01.197 --> 01:45:04.909
You say you're ashamed of me.
well. I'm ashamed of you!

824
01:45:05.076 --> 01:45:07.244
What the fuck was that back there?

825
01:45:07.411 --> 01:45:09.747
Where's your self-respect?

826
01:45:10.081 --> 01:45:13.084
Apologizing to those motherfuckers.

827
01:45:13.250 --> 01:45:15.086
And in their language...

828
01:45:15.252 --> 01:45:17.880
on our land!

829
01:45:19.048 --> 01:45:22.218
You want to know
what drove me to this?

830
01:45:23.010 --> 01:45:27.264
I'm tired. Tired of waiting.

831
01:45:27.932 --> 01:45:32.019
I'm tired watching you
just sit back and do nothing.

832
01:45:33.229 --> 01:45:38.484
You had your moment. But where's
mine? What the fuck do I get?

833
01:45:39.902 --> 01:45:42.655
Shaking down junkies for bit change?

834
01:45:42.822 --> 01:45:45.992
That's not the role of a future boss.

835
01:45:46.450 --> 01:45:49.370
That's not work you give a boss!

836
01:45:51.122 --> 01:45:53.624
You've destroyed us.

837
01:45:53.874 --> 01:45:56.127
You've destroyed everything.

838
01:45:59.714 --> 01:46:01.882
Dad.

839
01:46:02.049 --> 01:46:03.050
Dad.

840
01:46:03.217 --> 01:46:07.513
Dad. everything we've lost.

841
01:46:07.680 --> 01:46:09.598
We can get back.

842
01:46:09.765 --> 01:46:12.059
We can get it all back.

843
01:46:12.226 --> 01:46:14.687
Dad. trust in me. I can fix this.

844
01:46:14.854 --> 01:46:16.480
I can fix this.

845
01:46:16.647 --> 01:46:18.899
I can fix this.

846
01:46:20.943 --> 01:46:22.528
Okay. that's enough.

847
01:46:23.863 --> 01:46:25.614
Enough.

848
01:46:33.080 --> 01:46:36.584
<i>Eka. prepare a peace package
for the Gates.</i>

849
01:46:36.751 --> 01:46:39.253
We'll give them our land
in Menteng and Sabang.

850
01:46:39.503 --> 01:46:40.546
Got it?

851
01:46:40.713 --> 01:46:42.590
Yes. boss.

852
01:46:49.513 --> 01:46:51.766
You can't go in there. He's in...

853
01:47:17.041 --> 01:47:19.043
Forgive me.

854
01:47:55.871 --> 01:47:56.997
You fucking traitor.

855
01:48:13.389 --> 01:48:15.474
How could you do this. Uco?

856
01:48:43.919 --> 01:48:45.379
Eka. run!

857
01:49:22.583 --> 01:49:24.793
What do you want to do with him?

858
01:49:32.426 --> 01:49:34.345
Take him.

859
01:57:22.104 --> 01:57:23.689
What's that?

860
01:57:28.026 --> 01:57:29.611
Yeah. I understand.

861
01:57:31.154 --> 01:57:33.824
I'll call you back.

862
01:57:45.252 --> 01:57:49.339
Reza was just seen
entering Bejo's restaurant.

863
01:57:52.718 --> 01:57:54.886
I thought we'd secured his services.

864
01:57:55.721 --> 01:57:58.432
That was my understanding.

865
01:58:03.812 --> 01:58:06.273
Then why the fuck is he meeting Bejo?

866
01:58:15.198 --> 01:58:16.575
Well?

867
01:58:17.868 --> 01:58:19.578
Bejo...

868
01:58:19.745 --> 01:58:23.248
is a fucking nobody.
take care of him now.

869
01:58:25.959 --> 01:58:28.462
- As for Reza and the rest of them...
- Boss. wait.

870
01:58:31.757 --> 01:58:35.635
Bejo's not alone.

871
01:58:37.345 --> 01:58:39.097
He has Uco with him.

872
01:58:40.557 --> 01:58:43.435
Seems they joined forces...

873
01:58:43.602 --> 01:58:45.562
after taking out Bangun.

874
01:58:48.273 --> 01:58:50.192
Point blank to the head.

875
01:58:53.028 --> 01:58:54.654
Bejo...

876
01:58:55.447 --> 01:58:58.283
has serious numbers now.

877
01:58:58.909 --> 01:59:00.911
He's becoming a genuine threat.

878
01:59:04.247 --> 01:59:06.541
Anything is possible.

879
01:59:08.585 --> 01:59:09.795
What should we do?

880
01:59:09.961 --> 01:59:12.255
We go to war!

881
01:59:13.381 --> 01:59:15.884
If he pulled a trigger
on his own father...

882
01:59:16.760 --> 01:59:19.262
he won't hesitate to come for us.

883
01:59:20.472 --> 01:59:22.557
We start over.

884
01:59:25.852 --> 01:59:27.938
I want Uco and Bejo
in the ground by tonight.

885
01:59:29.881 --> 01:59:31.601
Reza and the rest of those crooks too.

886
01:59:31.708 --> 01:59:33.835
Wait a minute. you can't be serious!

887
01:59:35.654 --> 01:59:38.031
They're not cops anymore.

888
01:59:39.449 --> 01:59:41.409
They're in my world now.

889
02:00:03.682 --> 02:00:05.392
Eka! Eka!

890
02:00:11.523 --> 02:00:13.775
I know who you are.

891
02:00:13.942 --> 02:00:15.193
I know where you're from.

892
02:00:20.991 --> 02:00:23.118
I told you before...

893
02:00:25.161 --> 02:00:27.747
we come from the same place.

894
02:00:30.500 --> 02:00:32.168
I hope..

895
02:00:33.336 --> 02:00:35.630
Our fates don't end up the same.

896
02:00:39.384 --> 02:00:41.469
I don't care what they say.

897
02:00:43.638 --> 02:00:45.557
I'm not a traitor.

898
02:00:45.974 --> 02:00:47.559
I'm not a fucking criminal.

899
02:00:51.438 --> 02:00:53.315
There's no end to this.

900
02:00:55.191 --> 02:00:56.651
You try to run...

901
02:00:57.986 --> 02:00:59.946
they hound you down.

902
02:01:02.616 --> 02:01:04.784
They lose a head?

903
02:01:06.703 --> 02:01:08.830
It just grows right fucking back.

904
02:01:12.542 --> 02:01:14.252
If you want out...

905
02:01:17.172 --> 02:01:19.132
you put them down.

906
02:01:22.552 --> 02:01:23.553
All of them.

907
02:01:30.769 --> 02:01:31.978
Eka. wait.

908
02:02:38.127 --> 02:02:41.171
Why the fuck didn't you tell me you had
an undercover in there with Bangun?

909
02:02:41.338 --> 02:02:43.007
<i>What are you talking about?</i>

910
02:02:43.173 --> 02:02:44.675
Eka.

911
02:02:44.842 --> 02:02:46.301
<i>That piece of shit?</i>

912
02:02:46.468 --> 02:02:48.137
That piece of shit saved my life.

913
02:02:48.303 --> 02:02:53.976
<i>Yeah. he also cost the lives of 10
honest cops when he fed us bad intel.</i>

914
02:02:54.143 --> 02:02:56.520
<i>He went rogue. Rama.</i>

915
02:02:56.687 --> 02:02:59.690
And it never crossed your mind
to mention it to me?

916
02:03:00.107 --> 02:03:03.318
<i>Now's not the time for this.
The commissioner is dead.</i>

917
02:03:03.485 --> 02:03:05.654
<i>Fucking bodies are piling up
all over the city.</i>

918
02:03:07.031 --> 02:03:09.283
<i>There's no such thing as
a clean war. lieutenant.</i>

919
02:03:09.450 --> 02:03:12.745
Maybe not.
But we can trace it to Reza.

920
02:03:12.911 --> 02:03:15.164
We picked him up on Uco's wire.

921
02:03:17.082 --> 02:03:18.709
They're together?

922
02:03:18.876 --> 02:03:20.627
<i>As far as we know.</i>

923
02:03:20.794 --> 02:03:24.715
<i>We lost the signal.
but we're on our way.</i>

924
02:03:28.135 --> 02:03:30.387
I'm going to ask you one question.

925
02:03:30.554 --> 02:03:32.639
And it's the only answer I want.

926
02:03:33.474 --> 02:03:35.017
Is my family safe?

927
02:03:35.184 --> 02:03:37.102
<i>Yes. of course.</i>

928
02:03:38.687 --> 02:03:41.565
- Keep them that way.
- Wait. Rama. wait...

929
02:03:48.405 --> 02:03:50.157
Watch over me.

930
02:06:41.370 --> 02:06:43.580
Sir. would you like a tissue?

931
02:06:43.747 --> 02:06:45.907
You better come here
if you want your fucking tip.

932
02:06:45.949 --> 02:06:47.575
Yes. sir.

933
02:06:53.006 --> 02:06:54.549
I'm sorry. sir.

934
02:07:25.539 --> 02:07:28.625
Of course we can.

935
02:07:28.792 --> 02:07:30.836
We're the ones who will set it up.

936
02:07:31.920 --> 02:07:35.090
The important thing is the reward.

937
02:07:35.257 --> 02:07:38.385
New faces. New prices.

938
02:07:38.552 --> 02:07:40.053
New prices?

939
02:07:40.220 --> 02:07:42.931
Come on. Reza.

940
02:07:43.098 --> 02:07:45.934
Just think of it as a probation period.

941
02:07:47.602 --> 02:07:49.688
How much did Goto pay you?

942
02:07:50.105 --> 02:07:52.607
That's not a smart question to ask.

943
02:07:52.774 --> 02:07:55.736
Oh. yeah. and why's that?

944
02:07:55.902 --> 02:07:59.323
Because I'm meeting you. Not him.

945
02:07:59.489 --> 02:08:01.408
Now think up a number.

946
02:08:01.575 --> 02:08:05.120
If it keeps me here after dinner.
then it's enough.

947
02:08:09.708 --> 02:08:12.085
Hey. sidekick.

948
02:08:13.628 --> 02:08:15.964
You're talkative.

949
02:08:24.806 --> 02:08:26.725
Boss...

950
02:08:26.892 --> 02:08:29.019
he escaped from the car.

951
02:08:32.272 --> 02:08:33.899
Put the word out.

952
02:08:34.066 --> 02:08:36.526
Whoever finds him will be...

953
02:08:36.693 --> 02:08:38.195
He's here.

954
02:08:38.362 --> 02:08:40.280
He's coming up.

955
02:08:42.240 --> 02:08:45.202
- Then hold him off.
- Yes. boss.

956
02:08:47.204 --> 02:08:48.413
Everything okay?

957
02:08:53.126 --> 02:08:54.211
Take care of it.

958
02:09:05.514 --> 02:09:07.224
Reza...

959
02:09:08.141 --> 02:09:09.184
don't worry.

960
02:09:09.351 --> 02:09:11.770
Everything is under control.

961
02:09:11.937 --> 02:09:13.355
They are more than capable of...

962
02:09:16.441 --> 02:09:18.110
Motherfucker.

963
02:10:42.402 --> 02:10:43.403
Give me the ball.

964
02:10:51.620 --> 02:10:52.913
<i>As usual.</i>

965
02:12:14.494 --> 02:12:15.829
No!

966
02:20:34.535 --> 02:20:36.120
Reza!

967
02:25:43.427 --> 02:25:44.595
No...

968
02:25:47.640 --> 02:25:48.724
I'm done.
